2002-05-30	15:06	Denis Oliver Kropp <dok@directfb.org>

	Files:	src/gfx/generic/generic.c (1.64) (+53 -3)
	
	Sacc_to_Aop_rgb16 does aligned writes now, gives 1-3% on my Intel machine.
