2002-01-14	04:57	Denis Oliver Kropp <dok@directfb.org>

	Files:	include/directfb.h (1.69) (+164 -125)
		src/windows/idirectfbwindow.c (1.23) (+49 -168)
		src/media/idirectfbfont.c (1.20) (+25 -15)
