2001-06-27	13:58	Denis Oliver Kropp <dok@directfb.org>

	Files:	include/directfb.h (1.35) (+128 -34)
		src/misc/conf.h (1.7) (+2 -0)
		src/display/idirectfbsurface_layer.c (1.7) (+16 -13)
